casebody.data:
Monday, March 29, 1993

MOTION DOCKET

93-460. Celebrezze v. Baron.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus. Upon consideration of respondents’ request for clarification,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that briefing in this case is stayed pending further order of the court.

Wright, J., not participating.
